| Melt-Water Pulse 1B (supercharged)     | 12.4–11.4      | Ice-sheet collapse accelerated by cosmic-ray forcing                             | Final 60–80 m eustatic rise |
| Combined relative sea-level jump        | 12.8–11.4      | 130–170 m effective drowning of the shelf in < 800 years                         | Entire coastal empire erased |

